(1450, 3343, '_aviaLayoutBuilderCleanData', '[av_two_third first]\r\n[av_image src=''http://phfbd.com/projukti/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Qa-training1.jpg'' attachment=''3457'' attachment_size=''full'' align=''center'' animation=''no-animation'' styling='''' hover='''' link='''' target='''' caption='''' font_size='''' appearance='''' overlay_opacity=''0.4'' overlay_color=''#000000'' overlay_text_color=''#ffffff''][/av_image]\r\n\r\n[av_textblock size='''' font_color='''' color='''']\r\nProjukti Corporation Continuing Education offers a full suite of software testing and quality assurance courses that can be taken as standalone units or as part of our Software Test Engineer Certificate Program. These courses train students for entry-level software testing jobs, which require workers who can successfully find software bugs and provide logical, concise written reports on them. Our courses were developed by respected software test engineers and managers to target the skills critical to success in the software testing workplace.\r\n\r\nAs software becomes more complex, it is necessary to establish processes and clear methodologies. Doing so will ensure that the end-product has been exposed to intensive and rigorous industry-wide testing techniques and procedures.\r\n\r\nThis course is designed to help improve your job performance and the quality of your company''s software products. It is a broad course that addresses all of the body of knowledge area of the SQA. It provides a thorough introduction for those new to software quality, as well as an opportunity to fill in any blank spots for experienced personnel. Knowledge of and/or work experience within the software quality assurance field is helpful but not required. Although not designed as a certification refresher.\r\n\r\nWe Offer QA training for following categories:\r\n\r\n<center>[su_button url="http://phfbd.com/projukti/qa-professionals" style="glass" size="4" wide="no" center="no" icon="icon: arrow-circle-right"