'''' font_color='''' custom_title='''' custom_content='''' color='''' custom_bg='''' custom_font='''' custom_border='''']\r\nWhile a sales team works to close deals with small to large businesses, it is necessary to maintain individual accounts and keep track of contacts under them. Effective organization in interacting with your contacts, who may represent or account for a particular company or such other bigger concern is of high priority.\r\n[/av_icon_box]\r\n\r\n[/av_one_fourth][av_one_fourth]\r\n\r\n[av_icon_box position=''left'' boxed='''' icon=''ue80b'' font=''entypo-fontello'' title=''HR Management'' link='''' linktarget='''' linkelement='''' font_color='''' custom_title='''' custom_content='''' color='''' custom_bg='''' custom_font='''' custom_border='''']\r\n<div id="stcpDiv">\r\n<div id="stcpDiv">Human resource software to your company including higher productivity, fewer errors, and easier access to data. This makes managing all aspects of employee benefits easy, including eligibility and account information.</div>\r\n<div id="stcpDiv">Our software  can provide HR solutions for your company.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n[/av_icon_box]\r\n\r\n[/av_one_fourth][av_one_fourth]\r\n\r\n[av_icon_box position=''left'' boxed='''' icon=''ue859'' font=''entypo-fontello'' title=''General Sales'' link='''' linktarget='''' linkelement='''' font_color='''' custom_title='''' custom_content='''' color='''' custom_bg='''' custom_font='''' custom_border='''']\r\nGeneral Sales is a complete point of sale system that runs on any device. Inventory control makes the difference between profit and loss. We help you optimize your inventory to save money and increase sales. We''ve worked with our customers to create a system that most retailers can learn in minutes.\r\n[/av_icon_box]\r\n\r\n[/av_one_fourth][av_one_fourth]\r\n\r\n[av_icon_box position=''left'' boxed='''' icon=''ue852'' font=''entypo-fontello'' title=''Export Sales'' link='''' linktarget='''' linkelement='''' font_color='''' custom_title='''' custom_content='''' color='''' custom_bg='''' custom_font='''' custom_border='''']\r\nExport sales Software enrich with the various export modules of Pre-Sales, Costing, Materials management for RM, PM and FG, Loan Licensee & contract manufacturing and product status tracking and complete procurement and storage management with Regular Sales process with multiple currency management.\r\n[/av_icon_box]\r\n\r\n[/av_one_fourth][av_promobox button=''yes'' label=''Buy Now!'' link=''manually,http://phfbd.com/projukti/buy-now'' link_target='''' color=''aqua'' custom_bg=''#444444'' custom_font=''#ffffff'' size=''large'' icon_select=''yes'' icon=''ue859'' font=''entypo-fontello'' box_color='''' box_custom_font=''#ffffff'' box_custom_bg=''#444444'' box_custom_border=''#333333'']\r\nOur software solutions can enhance your sales, productivity & much more.\r\n[/av_promobox]\r\n\r\n[/av_section][av_section color=''main_color'' custom_bg='''' src='''' position=''top left'' repeat=''no-repeat'' attach=''scroll'' padding=''default'' shadow=''shadow'']\r\n[av_one_half first]\r\n\r\n[av_heading tag=''h4'' padding=''20'' heading=''Why Us?'' color=''meta-heading'' style='''' custom_font='''' size='''' subheading_active='''' subheading_size='''' custom_class='''']\r\n\r\n[av_textblock size='''' font_color='''' color='''']\r\nWe believe our core values of integrity, client satisfaction, innovation and intellect differentiate us from our competitors. Our focus on developing and maintaining a measurable client satisfaction program has created a company culture where each of our associates delivers world class service every day. We help you succeed by implementing these solutions and services that allow you to manage your programs more efficiently and effectively. The difference with Projukti is our cultural dedication to Client Satisfaction and to our Community.\r\n[/av_textblock]\r\n\r\n[av_progress bar_styling=''av-striped-bar'' bar_animation=''av-animated-bar'']\r\n[av_