(1315, 3266, '_aviaLayoutBuilderCleanData', '[av_layerslider id=''3'']\r\n\r\n[av_section min_height='''' min_height_px=''500px'' padding=''default'' shadow=''shadow'' bottom_border=''no-border-styling'' id='''' color=''alternate_color'' custom_bg='''' src='''' attachment='''' attachment_size='''' attach=''scroll'' position=''top left'' repeat=''no-repeat'' video='''' video_ratio=''16:9'' overlay_opacity=''0.5'' overlay_color='''' overlay_pattern='''' overlay_custom_pattern='''']\r\n\r\n[av_hr class=''invisible'' height=''25'' shadow=''no-shadow'' position=''center'' custom_border=''av-border-thin'' custom_width=''80%'' custom_border_color='''' custom_margin_top=''20px'' custom_margin_bottom=''20px'' icon_select=''no'' custom_icon_color='''' icon=''ue808'' font=''entypo-fontello'']\r\n\r\n[av_one_half first]\r\n\r\n[av_textblock size='''' font_color='''' color='''']\r\n<h2 style="text-align: right;">About Us</h2>\r\n[/av_textblock]\r\n\r\n[av_hr class=''short'' height=''70'' position=''right'']\r\n\r\n[av_textblock size='''' font_color='''' color='''']\r\nIt is not possible to deliver quality of product and even getting the outsourcing Software Developments/Quality Control projects without having expert QA professionals, proper infrastructure & tools. Having spectacular demand of QA in Bangladesh, having no decent QA training institute in our country, it is indeed to have only QA based organization in our country which will focused on Quality Assurance, Quality Control, IT Process Management, Certifying to Software Products along with Software Developments. So, Projukti is having all and this is why it is new and unique in Bangladesh. Projukti Corporation is founded in New York, USA in 2007. It is been registered against 8822 Parsons Blvd, Jamaica, New York 11432, USA.\r\n[/av_textblock]\r\n\r\n[av_hr class=''short'' height=''70'' position=''right'']\r\n\r\n[av_button label=''Check out our Team'' link=''manually,http://'' link_target='''' color=''theme-color-subtle'' custom_bg=''#444444'' custom_font=''#ffffff'' size=''large'' position=''right'' icon_select=''yes'' icon=''14'']\r\n\r\n[/av_one_half][av_one_half]\r\n\r\n[av_iconlist position=''left'' font_color='''' custom_title='''' custom_content='''' color='''' custom_bg='''' custom_font='''' custom_border='''']\r\n[av_iconlist_item title=''Software Quality Assurance'' link='''' linktarget='''' linkelement='''' icon=''ue918'' font=''entypo-fontello'']\r\nProjukti is having expert SQA Engineers and Testers with variety of expertise arena. SQA Engineers are international certified.\r\n[/av_iconlist_item]\r\n[av_iconlist_item title=''Software Development'' link='''' linktarget='''' linkelement='''' icon=''ue8d3'' font=''entypo-fontello'']\r\nAutomation process implementation is the key of our development team. Our team is expert on developing automated systems.\r\n[/av_iconlist_item]\r\n[av_iconlist_item title=''Web Development'' link='''' linktarget='''' linkelement='''' icon=''ue8b1'' font=''entypo-fontello'']\r\nOur web development team recognize the value of solid info design and branding that engages the customer at your site.\r\n[/av_iconlist_item]\r\n[av_iconlist_item title=''QA Training'' link='''' linktarget='''' linkelement='''' icon=''ue8c9'' font=''entypo-fontello'']\r\nInstructors have real world many years experience from USA. They visit Bangladesh to provide real world training.\r\n[/av_iconlist_item]\r\n[/av_iconlist]\r\n\r\n[/av_one_half][av_hr class=''custom'' height=''50'' shadow=''no-shadow'' position=''center'' custom_border=''av-border-thin'' custom_width=''80%'' custom_border_color='''' custom_margin_top=''20px'' custom_margin_bottom=''20px'' icon_select=''no'' custom_icon_color='''' icon=''ue808'' font=''entypo-fontello'']\r\n\r\n[av_textblock size='''' font_color='''' color='''']\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;">Our Product</h3>\r\n[/av_textblock]\r\n\r\n[av_hr class=''short'' height=''50'' shadow=''no-shadow'' position=''center'' custom_border=''av-border-thin'' custom_width=''50px'' custom_border_color='''' custom_margin_top=''30px'' custom_margin_bottom=''30px'' icon_select=''yes'' custom_icon_color='''' icon=''ue808'' font=''entypo-fontello'']\r\n\r\n[av_one_fourth first]\r\n\r\n[av_icon_box position=''left'' boxed='''' icon=''ue83a'' font=''entypo-fontello'' title=''Accounts management'' link='''' linktarget='''' linkelement='''' font_color='''' custom_title='''' custom_content='''' color='''' custom_bg='''' custom_font='''' custom_border='''']\r\nWhile a sales team works to close deals with small to large businesses, it is necessary to maintain individual accounts and keep track of contacts under them. Effective organization in interacting with your contacts, who may represent or account for a particular company or such other bigger concern is of high priority.\r\n[/av_icon_box]\r\n\r\n[/av_one_fourth][av_one_fourth]\r\n\r\n[av_icon_box position=''left'' boxed='''' icon=''ue80b'' font=''entypo-fontello'' title=''HR Management'' link='''' linktarget='''' linkelement='''' font_color='''' custom_title='''' custom_content='''' color='''' custom_bg='''' custom_font='''' custom_border='''']\r\nHuman resource software to your company including higher productivity, fewer errors, and easier access to data. This makes managing all aspects of employee benefits easy, including eligibility and account information.Our software can provide HR solutions for your company.\r\n[/av_icon_box]\r\n\r\n[/av_one_fourth][av_one_fourth]\r\n\r\n[av_icon_box position=''left'' boxed='''' icon=''ue859'' font=''entypo-fontello'' title=''General Sales'' link='''' linktarget='''' linkelement='''' font_color='''' custom_title='''' custom_content='''' color='''' custom_bg='''' custom_font='''' custom_border='''']\r\nGeneral Sales is a complete point of sale system that runs on any device. Inventory control makes the difference between profit and loss. We help you optimize your inventory to save money and increase sales. We''ve worked with our customers to create a system that most retailers can learn in minutes.\r\n[/av_icon_box]\r\n\r\n[/av_one_fourth][av_one_fourth]\r\n\r\n[av_icon_box position=''left'' boxed='''' icon=''ue852'' font=''entypo-fontello'' title=''Export Sales'' link='''' linktarget='''' linkelement='''' font_color='''' custom_title='''' custom_content='''' color='''' custom_bg='''' custom_font='''' custom_border='''']\r\nExport sales Software enrich with the various export modules of Pre-Sales, Costing, Materials management for RM, PM and FG, Loan Licensee & contract manufacturing and product status tracking and complete procurement and storage management with Regular Sales process with multiple currency management.\r\n[/av_icon_box]\r\n\r\n[/av_one_fourth][av_hr class=''invisible'' height=''50'' shadow=''no-shadow'' position=''center'' custom_border=''av-border-thin'' custom_width=''50px'' custom_border_color='''' custom_margin_top=''30px'' custom_margin_bottom=''30px'' icon_select=''yes'' custom_icon_color='''' icon=''ue808'' font=''entypo-fontello'']\r\n\r\n[av_promobox button=''yes'' label=''Buy Now!'' link=''manually,http://phfbd.com/projukti/buy-now'' link_target='''' color=''aqua'' custom_bg=''#444444'' custom_font=''#ffffff'' size=''large'' icon_select=''yes'' icon=''ue859'' font=''entypo-fontello'' box_color='''' box_custom_font=''#ffffff'' box_custom_bg=''#444444'' box_custom_border=''#333333'']\r\nOur software solutions can enhance your sales, productivity & much more.\r\n[/av_promobox]\r\n\r\n[av_one_half first]\r\n\r\n[av_heading tag=''h4'' padding=''20'' heading=''Why Us?'' color='''' style='''' custom_font='''' size='''' subheading_active='''' subheading_size=''15'' custom_class=''''][/av_heading]\r\n\r\n[av_textblock size='''' font_color='''' color='''']\r\nWe believe our core values of integrity, client satisfaction, innovation and intellect differentiate us from our competitors. Our focus on developing and maintaining a measurable client satisfaction program has crea