(1605, 3435, '_aviaLayoutBuilderCleanData', '[av_one_full first]\r\n\r\n[av_image src=''http://phfbd.com/projukti/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/placement-web-panner.jpg'' attachment=''3439'' attachment_size=''full'' align=''center'' animation=''no-animation'' styling='''' hover='''' link='''' target='''' caption='''' font_size='''' appearance='''' overlay_opacity=''0.4'' overlay_color=''#000000'' overlay_text_color=''#ffffff''][/av_image]\r\n\r\n[av_textblock size='''' font_color='''' color='''']\r\n \r\nThere are huge demands for QA professional worldwide. Bangladesh is blooming for the QA demands and it will be increased soon rapidly. Projukti is taking the initiative in advance to supply the demand on time.\r\n[/av_textblock]\r\n\r\n[av_heading tag=''h3'' padding=''10'' heading=''For Individuals'' color='''' style=''blockquote modern-quote modern-centered'' custom_font='''' size='''' subheading_active='''' subheading_size=''15'' custom_class=''''][/av_heading]\r\n\r\n[av_textblock size='''' font_color='''' color='''']\r\nWe provide the QA jobs for those trainees who pass all the exams with A+ & earn the USA certification for SQA through us. We also offer job to the right candidates to our company and sort list the experienced candidate for job placement national and worldwide.\r\n\r\nFolks who are already QA professional and looking for a job to either national or global market, please fell free to send your resume to  <a href="mailto:contact@projukti.net">contact<span id="cloak99582"></span><span id="cloak6293">@projukti.net</span></a>. After receiving the resume, we will contact you at our earliest convenient.For global market, candidiate need to have solid 5 years of QA experince or 10 years of IT experince in which 3 years should be in QA.\r\n[/av_textblock]\r\n\r\n[av_heading tag=''h3'' padding=''10'' heading=''For Corporates'' color='''' style=''blockquote modern-quote modern-centered'' custom_font='''' size='''' subheading_active='''' subheading_size=''15'' custom_class=''''][/av_heading]\r\n\r\n[av_textblock size='''' font_color='''' color='''']\r\nWe have many QA professions who have international QA certifications, who are experienced and got realworld traning from us. If any corporation is looking for QA professionals to hire, please email us to <a href="mailto:contact@projukti.net">contact@projukti.net</a>\r\n[/av_textblock]\r\n\r\n[/av_one_full]'),
