s, it is necessary to maintain individual accounts and keep track of contacts under them. Effective organization in interacting with your contacts, who may represent or account for a particular company or such other bigger concern is of high priority.\r\n[/av_icon_box]\r\n\r\n[/av_one_fourth][av_one_fourth]\r\n\r\n[av_icon_box position=''left'' boxed='''' icon=''ue80b'' font=''entypo-fontello'' title=''HR Management'' link='''' linktarget='''' linkelement='''' font_color='''' custom_title='''' custom_content='''' color='''' custom_bg='''' custom_font='''' custom_border='''']\r\nHuman resource software to your company including higher productivity, fewer errors, and easier access to data. This makes managing all aspects of employee benefits easy, including eligibility and account information.Our software can provide HR solutions for your company.\r\n[/av_icon_box]\r\n\r\n[/av_one_fourth][av_one_fourth]\r\n\r\n[av_icon_box position=''left'' boxed='''' icon=''ue859'' font=''entypo-fontello'' title=''General Sales'' link='''' linktarget='''' linkelement='''' font_color='''' custom_title='''' custom_content='''' color='''' custom_bg='''' custom_font='''' custom_border='''']\r\nGeneral Sales is a complete point of sale system that runs on any device. Inventory control makes the difference between profit and loss. We help you optimize your inventory to save money and increase sales. We''ve worked with our customers to create a system that most retailers can learn in minutes.\r\n[/av_icon_box]\r\n\r\n[/av_one_fourth][av_one_fourth]\r\n\r\n[av_icon_box position=''left'' boxed='''' icon=''ue852'' font=''entypo-fontello'' title=''Export Sales'' link='''' linktarget='''' linkelement='''' font_color='''' custom_title='''' custom_content='''' color='''' custom_bg='''' custom_font='''' custom_border='''']\r\nExport sales Software enrich with the various export modules of Pre-Sales, Costing, Materials management for RM, PM and FG, Loan Licensee &amp; contract manufacturing and prod