\n\r\n[av_one_fourth first]\r\n\r\n[av_icon_box position=''left'' boxed='''' icon=''ue83a'' font=''entypo-fontello'' title=''Accounts management'' link='''' linktarget='''' linkelement='''' font_color='''' custom_title='''' custom_content='''' color='''' custom_bg='''' custom_font='''' custom_border='''']\r\nWhile a sales team works to close deals with small to large businesses, it is necessary to maintain individual accounts and keep track of contacts under them. Effective organization in interacting with your contacts, who may represent or account for a particular company or such other bigger concern is of high priority.\r\n[/av_icon_box]\r\n\r\n[/av_one_fourth][av_one_fourth]\r\n\r\n[av_icon_box position=''left'' boxed='''' icon=''ue80b'' font=''entypo-fontello'' title=''HR Management'' link='''' linktarget='''' linkelement='''' font_color='''' custom_title='''' custom_content='''' color='''' custom_bg='''' custom_font='''' custom_border='''']\r\nHuman resource software to your company including higher productivity, fewer errors, and easier access to data. This makes managing all aspects of employee benefits easy, including eligibility and account information.Our software can provide HR solutions for your company.\r\n[/av_icon_box]\r\n\r\n[/av_one_fourth][av_one_fourth]\r\n\r\n[av_icon_box position=''left'' boxed='''' icon=''ue859'' font=''entypo-fontello'' title=''General Sales'' link='''' linktarget='''' linkelement='''' font_color='''' custom_title='''' custom_content='''' color='''' custom_bg='''' custom_font='''' custom_border='''']\r\nGeneral Sales is a complete point of sale system that runs on any device. Inventory control makes the difference between profit and loss. We help you optimize your inventory to save money and increase sales. We''ve worked with our customers to create a system that most retailers can learn in minutes.\r\n[/av_icon_box]\r\n\r\n[/av_one_fourth][av_one_fourth]\r\n\r\n[av_icon_box position=''left'' boxed='''' icon=''ue852'' font=''entypo-fontello'' title=''Export Sales'' link='''' linktarget='''' linkelement='''' font_color='''' custom_title='''' custom_content='''' color='''' custom_bg='''' custom_font='''' custom_border='''']\r\nExport sales Software enrich with the various export modules of Pre-Sales, Costing, Materials management for RM, PM and FG, Loan Licensee &amp; contract manufacturing and product status tracking and complete procurement and storage management with Regular Sales process with multiple currency management.\r\n[/av_icon_box]\r\n\r\n[/av_one_fourth][av_promobox button=''yes'' label=''Buy Now!'' link=''manually,http://phfbd.com/projukti/buy-now'' link_target='''' color=''aqua'' custom_bg=''#444444'' custom_font=''#ffffff'' size=''large'' icon_select=''yes'' icon=''ue859'' font=''entypo-fontello'' box_color='''' box_custom_font=''#ffffff'' box_custom_bg=''#444444'' box_custom_border=''#333333'']\r\nOur software solutions can enhance your sales, productivity &amp; much more.\r\n[/av_promobox]\r\n[/av_section]\r\n\r\n[av_section min_height='''' min_height_px=''500px'' padding=''default'' shadow=''no-shadow'' bottom_border=''no-border-styling'' scroll_down='''' id='''' color=''main_color'' custom_bg='''' src='''' attach=''scroll'' position=''top left'' repeat=''no-repeat'' video='''' video_ratio=''16:9'' video_mobile_disabled='''' overlay_enable='''' overlay_opacity=''0.5'' overlay_color='''' overlay_pattern='''' overlay_custom_pattern='''']\r\n\r\n[av_one_half first]\r\n\r\n[av_heading tag=''h4'' padding=''20'' heading=''Why Us?'' color='''' style='''' custom_font='''' size='''' subheading_active='''' subheading_size=''15'' custom_class=''''][/av_heading]\r\n\r\n[av_textblock size='''' font_color='''' color='''']\r\nWe believe our core values of integrity, client satisfaction, innovation and intellect differentiate us from our competitors. Our focus on developing and maintaining a measurable client satisfaction program has created a company culture where each of our associates delivers world class service every day. We help you succeed by implementing these solutions and services that allow you to manage your programs more efficiently and effectively. The difference with Projukti is our cultural dedication to Client Satisfaction and to our Community.\r\n[/av_textblock]\r\n\r\n[av_progress bar_styling=''av-striped-bar'' bar_animation=''av-animated-bar'']\r\n[av_progress_bar title=''SQA'' progress=''99'' color=''theme-color'' icon_select=''yes'' icon=''ue918'' font=''entypo-fontello'']\r\n[av_progress_bar title=''Java'' progress=''95'' color=''blue'' icon_select=''yes'' icon=''ue8cf'' font=''entypo-fontello'']\r\n[av_progress_bar title=''C#'' progress=''90'' color=''theme-color'' icon_select=''yes'' icon=''ue922'' font=''entypo-fontello'']\r\n[av_progress_bar title=''PHP'' progress=''85'' color=''blue'' icon_select=''yes'' icon=''ue911'' font=''entypo-fontello'']\r\n[av_progress_bar title=''ASP.NET'' progress=''80'' color=''theme-color'' icon_select=''yes'' icon=''ue922'' font=''entypo-fontello'']\r\n[av_progress_bar title=''WordPress'' progress=''95'' color=''blue'' icon_select=''yes'' icon=''ue925'' font=''entypo-fontello'']\r\n[/av_progress]\r\n\r\n[av_textblock size='''' font_color='''' color='''']\r\nWhen you choose to do business with Projukti you are partnering with a company who cares. We are continually focused on finding ways to support our community and we participate in several philanthropic activities throughout the year. Our attitude toward great service and helping others makes our culture inviting and fun. We are always looking for the brightest and most talented people around to join us in servicing our clients and community.\r\n[/av_textblock]\r\n\r\n[/av_one_half][av_one_half]\r\n\r\n[av_heading tag=''h4'' padding=''20'' heading=''Get in Touch'' color='''' style='''' custom_font='''' size='''' subheading_active='''' subheading_size=''15'' custom_class=''''][/av_heading]\r\n\r\n[av_contact email=''suuaas@live.com'' title=''Send us mail'' button=''Submit'' on_send='''' sent=''Your message has been sent!'' link=''manually,http://'' subject='''' autorespond='''' captcha=''active'' color='''']\r\n[av_contact_field label=''Name'' type=''text'' options='''' check=''is_empty'' width=''element_half'' multi_select=''''][/av_contact_field]\r\n[av_contact_field label=''E-Mail'' type=''text'' options='''' check=''is_email'' width=''element_half'' multi_select=''''][/av_contact_field]\r\n[av_contact_field label=''Message'' type=''textarea'' check=''is_empty'' options='''' multi_select='''' width=''''][/av_contact_field]\r\n[/av_contact]\r\n\r\n[/av_one_half][/av_section]', 'Home F', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '3266-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-04-29 12:43:49', '2015-04-29 12:43:49', '', 3266, 'http://phfbd.com/projukti/2015/04/29/3266-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
